{"tid":2360343,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"凍到頭痛","createTime":"2021-01-09T15:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T17:51:18.000Z","uid":373951,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e21cfadf9c86921e560297058353573ca2b714e","tid":2360343,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"有無人長期血壓低，會頭暈。試過有次落車，突然眼前一黑個種。覺得天旋地轉，咩都睇唔到。個陣以為自己會死，個死亡感覺勁真實。有時覺得自己會隨時死，死因心肌梗塞缺氧，猝死。<br />\n<br />\n好易攰，唔想食野。今日得七度定八度，好凍......。前幾日十幾度，仲係間房到著短袖飲凍可樂。放假開始就唔想離開張被，訓十個鐘補眠都好攰。天氣凍，更加頭痛頭暈。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年都好殘廢Feel，身體差左好多。細個以為自己身體好好，十幾年左右先發一次燒。要不要去醫院檢查一下，離地獄不遠了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f1dac27dbca79f2158c5cc2da9c0fc2ba4edac","tid":2360343,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"有冇做運動同食得足夠？"},{"pid":"d51cd30d2fcfb4d404b48a1da120483343679606","tid":2360343,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6dad46d26f39e068e77a3838d1e068be0283ec","tid":2360343,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3f1dac27dbca79f2158c5cc2da9c0fc2ba4edac","tid":2360343,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"有冇做運動同食得足夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"無做運動 唔想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a8cd2718e26e52f9b31940195a3b0685bee1ed","tid":2360343,"uid":384177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6dad46d26f39e068e77a3838d1e068be0283ec","tid":2360343,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3f1dac27dbca79f2158c5cc2da9c0fc2ba4edac","tid":2360343,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"有冇做運動同食得足夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"無做運動 唔想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"你似係有低溫症wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e7959b3480cf01c122e0dc3dc7808f94609a6b","tid":2360343,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a8cd2718e26e52f9b31940195a3b0685bee1ed","tid":2360343,"uid":384177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6dad46d26f39e068e77a3838d1e068be0283ec","tid":2360343,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3f1dac27dbca79f2158c5cc2da9c0fc2ba4edac","tid":2360343,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"有冇做運動同食得足夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"無做運動 唔想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"你似係有低溫症wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b89a6fafbd59231bc0a41ed864700d5c897038","tid":2360343,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"試過坐或者瞓喺度一耐起身嗰吓都會眼前一黑 大約三五秒咁上下"},{"pid":"70cc3ddd18969bdb6f00d53ca6288c69bc70e3f1","tid":2360343,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:58:43.000Z","msg":"樓主勁廢"},{"pid":"8927f0fe38f7a0708766d377102a6a92b10b6322","tid":2360343,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:51:18.000Z","msg":"知係凍搞到咁就戴帽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依幾日凍我係屋企都會戴帽,唔戴真係會凍到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}